ComicInfo.Summary: Ben Santini, the leader of the Black Razors, reveals to his priest that he fears that he will kill the man that injured him many months ago, Lord Emp. The Black Razors then undergo their mission, to stop the Daemonites from attacking important industrialists, and find out that a Daemonite with shape-shifting abilities is masquerading as a member of the WildC.A.T.s. The Razors attack the WildC.A.T.s in the hope of exposing the masquerade. They eventually learn that Maul is the one being impersonated and Ben Santini is left with a problem: attack the Daemonite or kill Lord Emp, the man he blames for the misery in his life. He shoots the Daemonite and lets the WildC.A.T.s to ponder where the real Maul is.
